02:30:45.240 --> 02:30:47.240
Love is what people live for.

02:30:47.240 --> 02:30:49.240
And in my story,

02:30:49.240 --> 02:30:52.240
it's sort of what they die for.

02:30:52.240 --> 02:30:55.350
Submitted for the approval

02:30:55.350 --> 02:30:57.350
of the Midnight Society,

02:30:57.350 --> 02:30:59.350
I call this story

02:30:59.350 --> 02:31:06.930
the tale of the dream girl.

02:31:06.930 --> 02:31:09.750
Johnny and Erica

02:31:09.750 --> 02:31:10.750
were brother and sister,

02:31:10.750 --> 02:31:12.750
and they were really close.

02:31:13.750 --> 02:31:15.750
Yeah!

02:31:15.750 --> 02:31:17.750
Come on, it's quarter after.

02:31:17.750 --> 02:31:18.750
I've got a ton of homework

02:31:18.750 --> 02:31:19.750
and we've got to close out.

02:31:19.750 --> 02:31:20.750
Yeah, yeah.

02:31:20.750 --> 02:31:21.750
I just finished lubing the pin setter.

02:31:21.750 --> 02:31:23.750
I got to make sure it won't crash on me.

02:31:23.750 --> 02:31:24.750
Yeah, right.

02:31:24.750 --> 02:31:25.750
You're just playing.

02:31:25.750 --> 02:31:27.750
They even worked it at the same place.

02:31:27.750 --> 02:31:29.750
The Bola Ramilanes.

02:31:29.750 --> 02:31:30.750
Yeah!

02:31:30.750 --> 02:31:32.750
Perfect.

02:31:32.750 --> 02:31:33.750
As usual.

02:31:33.750 --> 02:31:35.750
And modest too.

02:31:35.750 --> 02:31:36.750
Hey.

02:31:36.750 --> 02:31:37.750
Did I ever tell you

02:31:37.750 --> 02:31:39.750
you're my favorite sister?

02:31:39.750 --> 02:31:41.750
I'm your only sister.

02:31:42.750 --> 02:31:43.750
Yeah.

02:31:43.750 --> 02:31:45.750
Hurry up.

02:31:45.750 --> 02:31:47.750
Erica was a waitress.

02:31:47.750 --> 02:31:49.750
Johnny, the repair guy.

02:31:49.750 --> 02:31:53.700
Come in or what?

02:31:53.700 --> 02:31:54.700
Yeah, yeah.

02:31:54.700 --> 02:31:55.700
You put this in here?

02:31:55.700 --> 02:31:56.700
Nope.

02:31:56.700 --> 02:31:57.700
Hmm.

02:31:57.700 --> 02:31:58.700
It's the girl's ring.

02:31:58.700 --> 02:32:00.700
