02:32:01.700 --> 02:32:02.700
Really?

02:32:02.700 --> 02:32:05.420
Great.

02:32:05.420 --> 02:32:07.420
Now you can go study with yourself.

02:32:07.420 --> 02:32:08.420
Hardy-har-har.

02:32:08.420 --> 02:32:10.420
Reach in the front.

02:32:10.420 --> 02:32:15.210
No, I can't get this thing off.

02:32:15.210 --> 02:32:16.210
Johnny!

02:32:16.210 --> 02:32:17.210
