02:32:18.210 --> 02:32:20.210
Don't you try salt?

02:32:20.210 --> 02:32:23.210
I tried everything except cutting my finger off.

02:32:23.210 --> 02:32:24.210
Bed time.

02:32:24.210 --> 02:32:25.210
School tomorrow.

02:32:25.210 --> 02:32:26.210
Come on, Mom.

02:32:26.210 --> 02:32:27.210
I've still got it.

02:32:27.210 --> 02:32:28.210
Erica, please.

02:32:28.210 --> 02:32:29.210
Don't argue.

02:32:30.210 --> 02:32:31.210
It's late.

02:32:32.210 --> 02:32:33.210
Good night, Mom.

02:32:34.210 --> 02:32:36.210
Jeez, what's the matter with her?

02:32:36.210 --> 02:32:40.210
Oh, she's got a lot on her mind.

02:32:40.210 --> 02:32:42.210
Yeah, I guess so.

02:32:42.210 --> 02:32:43.210
So you come in or what?

02:32:43.210 --> 02:32:45.210
No, I'm gonna do a little channel surfing.

02:32:45.210 --> 02:32:47.210
Get the light, will you?

02:32:47.210 --> 02:32:48.210
Good night.

02:32:55.730 --> 02:32:56.730
Johnny?

02:32:56.730 --> 02:32:59.460
Johnny, where are you?

02:32:59.460 --> 02:33:24.520
Oh, man.

02:33:24.520 --> 02:33:39.770
Give me a cola, would you, Erica?

02:33:39.770 --> 02:33:45.270
Man, I am living a charmed life.

02:33:45.270 --> 02:33:46.270
Really?

02:33:46.270 --> 02:33:47.270
Why?

02:33:47.270 --> 02:33:50.270
Just closed out another month without having to hire another maintenance guy?

02:33:50.270 --> 02:33:53.270
We haven't had a breakdown in four months.

02:33:53.270 --> 02:33:57.270
The longer I hold off hiring somebody, the better my books look.

02:33:57.270 --> 02:33:59.270
The better I look.

02:33:59.270 --> 02:34:01.270
Life is sweet.

02:34:01.270 --> 02:34:11.720
Yeah, thanks to me.

02:34:11.720 --> 02:34:13.720
What are you doing out here?

02:34:13.720 --> 02:34:15.720
Why can't I come out here?

02:34:15.720 --> 02:34:18.720
Uh, he'll pitch a fit if you get grease on him.

02:34:18.720 --> 02:34:19.720
Well, good.

02:34:19.720 --> 02:34:21.720
At least he'll know I'm around.

02:34:21.720 --> 02:34:23.720
Who does he think keeps this place running anyway?

02:34:23.720 --> 02:34:24.720
Don't worry about it.

02:34:24.720 --> 02:34:26.720
Erica, I can't do it all myself.

02:34:26.720 --> 02:34:28.720
I swear, if you didn't...

02:34:28.720 --> 02:34:29.720
What?

02:34:29.720 --> 02:34:35.600
You promise not to laugh if I tell you something?

02:34:35.600 --> 02:34:36.600
No.

02:34:38.980 --> 02:34:41.980
I've been having these really weird dreams lately.

02:34:41.980 --> 02:34:46.980
About this beautiful girl with long hair and amazing eyes.

02:34:46.980 --> 02:34:47.980
Yeah, so?

02:34:47.980 --> 02:34:48.980
You and every other guy?

02:34:48.980 --> 02:34:50.980
Yeah, but it's so real.

02:34:50.980 --> 02:34:52.980
You know, I've never seen her before.

02:34:52.980 --> 02:34:55.980
And I can't stop thinking about her.

02:34:55.980 --> 02:35:00.980
And she looks a lot like that girl over there.

02:35:00.980 --> 02:35:02.980
Cheryl Lighthart?

02:35:02.980 --> 02:35:03.980
I know.

02:35:03.980 --> 02:35:05.980
I know it sounds stupid.

02:35:05.980 --> 02:35:08.980
But maybe this dream is some kind of sign.

02:35:09.980 --> 02:35:11.980
This could be fate.

02:35:11.980 --> 02:35:12.980
Johnny, wait!

02:35:12.980 --> 02:35:14.980
It's okay, Elaine.

02:35:14.980 --> 02:35:16.980
I'll handle it.

02:35:16.980 --> 02:35:18.980
And how may I help you, ladies?

02:35:18.980 --> 02:35:21.980
I set a size six, not a size nine.

02:35:21.980 --> 02:35:23.980
What are your eyes upside down?

02:35:25.980 --> 02:35:27.980
Hi, Cheryl.

02:35:27.980 --> 02:35:28.980
You don't know me.

02:35:28.980 --> 02:35:30.980
And I don't know how to say this, but...

02:35:30.980 --> 02:35:38.580
You guys hear someone talking to me?

02:35:38.580 --> 02:35:39.580
I don't see anyone.

02:35:39.580 --> 02:35:40.580
Must be your imagination.

02:35:40.580 --> 02:35:42.580
Come on, let's go.

02:35:42.580 --> 02:35:46.990
Must be great to be so perfect.

02:35:46.990 --> 02:35:47.990
Yeah.

02:35:47.990 --> 02:36:12.900
Where's my stuff?

02:36:12.900 --> 02:36:34.480
It's me.

02:36:34.480 --> 02:36:35.480
It's Donna.

02:36:35.480 --> 02:36:36.480
Don't...

02:36:36.480 --> 02:37:32.520
Bills.

02:37:32.520 --> 02:37:33.520
What a surprise.

02:37:33.520 --> 02:37:34.520
More bill.

02:37:34.520 --> 02:37:35.520
Hey, Mom.

02:37:35.520 --> 02:37:39.050
Mom.

02:37:39.050 --> 02:37:41.050
I forgot this.

02:37:41.050 --> 02:37:56.830
Erica.

02:37:56.830 --> 02:38:00.180
Roses are red.

02:38:00.180 --> 02:38:01.180
Violets are blue.

02:38:01.180 --> 02:38:04.180
You know I'll never stop thinking of you.

02:38:04.180 --> 02:38:05.180
Of Donna Mainland.

02:38:05.180 --> 02:38:07.180
