02:38:25.740 --> 02:38:31.450
You have to see her, Erica.

02:38:31.450 --> 02:38:33.450
She's so beautiful.

02:38:33.450 --> 02:38:35.450
There's just something about her.

02:38:35.450 --> 02:38:37.450
